ls that schedule blocks or restrict visibility by user role and other conditions.'=>'Konfigurasikan kontrol tampilan yang menjadwalkan blok atau membatasi visibilitas berdasarkan peran pengguna dan kondisi lainnya.','Presets'=>'Preset','Controls'=>'Kontrol','Enable or disable controls for all blocks'=>'Aktifkan atau nonaktifkan kontrol untuk semua blok','Save Blocks'=>'Simpan Blok','Schedule'=>'Jadwalkan','Choose when to start showing and/or stop showing your blocks.'=>'Pilih dimana mulai ditampilkan dan/atau berhenti menampilkan blok anda.','This block control is available on:'=>'Blok kontrol ini sekarang tersedia di:','Post'=>'Postingan','Widgets'=>'Widget','Site Editor'=>'Editor Situs','User roles'=>'Peran Pengguna','Choose which users can see your blocks.'=>'Pilih pengguna mana yang dapat melihat blok Anda.','Device Type'=>'Tipe Perangkat','Choose the device type to show your blocks on.'=>'Pilih tipe perangkat untuk menampilkan blok Anda.','Device Width'=>'Lebar Perangkat','Choose the device width to show your blocks on.'=>'Pilih lebar perangkat untuk menampilkan blok Anda.','Term archives'=>'Arsip term','Choose on which taxonomies and terms archive pages your blocks can be displayed.'=>'Pilih dimana taksonomi dan halaman arsip term untuk blok anda akan ditampilkan.','Pages'=>'Laman','Choose in which pages your blocks can be displayed.'=>'Pilih dimana halaman untuk blok anda akan ditampilkan.','Browser & Device'=>'Peramban & Perangkat','Choose which browsers and devices can see your blocks.'=>'Pilih peramban dan perangkat mana yang dapat melihat blok Anda.','Operating System'=>'Sistem Operasi','Choose which operating systems can see your blocks.'=>'Pilih sistem operasi mana yang dapat melihat blok Anda.','Cookie'=>'Cookie','Show or hide blocks based on cookie values.'=>'Tampilkan atau sembunyikan blok berdasarkan nilai cookie.','User Meta'=>'Meta Pengguna','Show or hide blocks based on user meta values.'=>'Tampilkan atau sembunyikan blok berdasarkan nilai meta pengguna.','Post Meta'=>'Meta Post','Show or hide blocks based on post meta values.'=>'Tampilkan atau sembunyikan blok berdasarkan nilai meta post.','Query String'=>'String Kuery','Show or hide blocks based on URL query parameters.'=>'Tampilkan atau sembunyikan blok berdasarkan parameter kuery URL.','Capabilities'=>'Kemampuan','Show or hide blocks based on user capabilities.'=>'Tampilkan atau sembunyikan blok berdasarkan kemampuan pengguna.','Save Controls'=>'Simpan Kontrol','Loading presets...'=>'Memuat preset...','Accordion - PublishPress'=>'Accordion - PublishPress','Button - PublishPress'=>'Tombol - PublishPress','Icon - PublishPress'=>'Ikon - PublishPress','Image - PublishPress'=>'Gambar - PublishPress','List - PublishPress'=>'Daftar - PublishPress','Table - PublishPress'=>'Tabel - PublishPress','Tabs - PublishPress'=>'Tabulasi - PublishPress','Video - PublishPress'=>'Video - PublishPress','Columns - PublishPress'=>'Kolom kolom - PublishPress','Column - PublishPress'=>'Kolom - PublishPress','Contact Form - PublishPress'=>'Formulir Kontak - PublishPress','Count Up - PublishPress'=>'Hitung Naik - PublishPress','Images Slider - PublishPress'=>'Gambar Slider - PublishPress','Info Box - PublishPress'=>'Kotak Info - PublishPress','Map - PublishPress'=>'Peta - PublishPress','Newsletter - PublishPress'=>'Buletin - PublishPress','Social Links - PublishPress'=>'Tautan Sosial - PublishPress','Table of Contents - PublishPress'=>'Tabel Konten - PublishPress','Testimonial - PublishPress'=>'Testimoni - PublishPress','Woo Products - PublishPress'=>'Produk Woo - PublishPress','Show content in collapsible panels that expand when clicked.'=>'Tampilkan konten dalam panel yang dapat dilipat yang berkembang saat diklik.','Add a customizable call-to-action button with colors, sizes and icons.'=>'Tambahkan tombol ajakan bertindak yang dapat disesuaikan dengan warna, ukuran, dan ikon.','Insert a vector icon from a large library, with size and color controls.'=>'Sisipkan ikon vektor dari