gh Contact form blocks.'=>'Data disimpan melalui blok formulir kontak.','CSV'=>'CSV','JSON'=>'JSON','Download Newsletter Form data'=>'Unduh data formulir Newsletter','Data stored through Newsletter form blocks.'=>'Data disimpan melalui blok formulir newsletter.','These email settings apply to messages sent through PublishPress Contact form block.'=>'Pengaturan email ini berlaku untuk pesan yang dikirim melalui blok formulir kontak PublishPress.','Sender name'=>'Nama pengirim','Sender email'=>'Pengirim e-mail','Email title'=>'Judul e-mail','Email receiver'=>'Penerima e-mail','Save Form Settings'=>'Simpan Pengaturan Formulir','Blocks icon color'=>'Warna blok ikon','Apply in admin to blocks from PublishPress Blocks plugin.'=>'Terapkan di administrator untuk blok dari plugin PublishPress Blocks.','Save Settings'=>'Simpan Pengaturan','Legacy Blocks'=>'Blok Warisan','These older blocks are turned off by default on new sites. Enable any you want to use in the editor.'=>'Blok-blok lama ini dimatikan secara default di situs baru. Aktifkan yang ingin Anda gunakan di editor.','Enable the %s block'=>'Aktifkan blok %s','Legacy Features'=>'Fitur Warisan','Older features, turned off by default on new sites.'=>'Fitur-fitur lama, dimatikan secara default di situs baru.','Gallery lightbox'=>'Galeri lightbox','Open gallery images as a lightbox style popup'=>'Buka gambar galeri sebagai popup lightbox','Image caption'=>'Keterangan Gambar','Disabled'=>'Nonaktif','Overlay'=>'Lapisan atas','Display caption text on images loaded as lightbox in galleries.'=>'Tampilkan teks keterangan pada gambar yang dimuat sebagai lightbox dalam galeri.','Save Legacy Settings'=>'Simpan Pengaturan Warisan','Google API key'=>'Kunci Google API','How to create a Google API Key'=>'Bagaimana cara membuat kunci Google API?','A Google API key is required to use the Map block without any warning.'=>'Dibutuhkan API key dari Google untuk menggunakan blok peta tanpa peringatan.','Save Maps Settings'=>'Simpan pengaturan